snippet.title: Ultimate FPS Challenge (FPS Shooter Game 2023 Made in Unity 3D) | Few Minutes of Gameplay
snippet.description:
Here is a Few minutes of Gameplay video of my Latest FPS game, Ultimate FPS Challenge. 

The Game gives you the hardest fps challenge. You need to kill all targets and Especially Boses in each stage in order to progress further at the end You need to kill the Final Boss in order to complete the challenge. 

The Game have 5 Stages each with small enemies and one Unqiue Boss. 
Stage 1 - Remen Thrower 
Stage 2 - Marker Thrower 
Stage 3 - Tall Boss 
Stage 4 - Wedding Ring Thrower 
Final Stage - Dumbell Thrower

Game Download Link: https://mohd-asif.itch.io/ultimate-fps-challenge

Game is Free to Download & Source is also available in the same link for Download for 59.99$
